sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant API as TicketViewSet
    participant TSvc as TicketService
    participant MSvc as MessageService
    participant Admin
    participant Agent
    Customer->>UI: Create ticket
    UI->>API: POST /api/tickets/
    API->>TSvc: create_ticket()
    TSvc-->>UI: OPEN ticket
    Admin->>UI: Assign agent
    UI->>API: PATCH /tickets/{id}/assign/
    API->>TSvc: assign_agent_to_ticket()
    Agent->>UI: Change status OPEN to IN_PROGRESS
    UI->>API: PATCH /change_status/
    API->>TSvc: change_ticket_status()
    Agent->>UI: Reply message
    UI->>API: POST /api/messages/
    API->>MSvc: create_message()
    Agent->>UI: Change status to RESOLVED then CLOSED
    UI->>API: PATCH /change_status/
    Note over TSvc: CLOSED reopen only by admin
